{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sendBadges:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSInteger","text":"NSInteger"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"badge","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"badge","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The current application badge number (0 to clear badge)."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Reports the current badge count to Pushwoosh for analytics and to enable"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"badge-based segmentation. This is useful for:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Analytics"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Track user engagement through unread counts"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Segmentation","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Target users with high\/low badge counts"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Badge management"}]},{"text":": Allow server-side badge manipulation","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Call this method whenever you update the app badge to keep Pushwoosh in sync."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Example","type":"heading","text":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sync badge with Pushwoosh when updating unread counts:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class NotificationBadgeManager {","","    private(set) var unreadCount: Int = 0 {","        didSet {","            updateBadge()","        }","    }","","    func markAsRead(_ notificationIds: [String]) {","        unreadCount = max(0, unreadCount - notificationIds.count)","    }","","    func handleNewNotification() {","        unreadCount += 1","    }","","    func clearAll() {","        unreadCount = 0","    }","","    private func updateBadge() {","        \/\/ Update system badge","        if #available(iOS 16.0, *) {","            UNUserNotificationCenter.current().setBadgeCount(unreadCount)","        } else {","            UIApplication.shared.applicationIconBadgeNumber = unreadCount","        }","","        \/\/ Sync with Pushwoosh","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(unreadCount)","    }","}","","\/\/ Usage in AppDelegate","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func applicationDidBecomeActive(_ application: UIApplication) {","        \/\/ Sync current badge state when app becomes active","        let currentBadge = application.applicationIconBadgeNumber","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(currentBadge)","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/sendBadges:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sendBadges:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"sendBadges:"}],"title":"sendBadges:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)sendBadges:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol"},"abstract":[{"text":"Synchronizes the application badge number with Pushwoosh servers.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/sendbadges:"]}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc: